        ColorTools[🛠️ Essential Tools<br/>━━━━━━━━━━━━━<br/>• Lift/Gamma/Gain wheels<br/>• Curves for precision<br/>• Qualifiers for selection<br/>• Scopes for accuracy<br/>• Color warper for creative looks]
    end
    
    Color --> ColorPage
    NodeTree --> Node1
    Node1 --> Node2
    Node2 --> Node3
    Node3 --> ColorTools
